description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Runner's Program #8 of 9' from the channel Christie Wang.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement. The The Endorphin Wave vibe means Elevated energy, feel-good movement, steady build. This is especially good for When you want a challenging but steady burn..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Strengthen your hips and core with Christie in this runners-focused Pilates session. Explicit lyrics....
